<div class="portlet">
  <h2>Bug tracking</h2>

  <div class="portletBody portletContent" i18n:translate="malone-blurb"
      tal:define="vhosts
        modules/canonical.launchpad.webapp.vhosts/allvhosts/configs">
    <p>
    <img alt="" src="/@@/bug" />
    <a i18n:attributes="title" title="Malone"
        tal:attributes="href vhosts/bugs/rooturl"
        href="/bugs" i18n:translate="">Malone</a> is a
    <strong>collaborative bug tracker</strong> that allows the same bug to be
    tracked in different distributions and products.
    </p>

    <p>You can use Malone as your primary bug tracker. It offers both web-based
    and email interfaces, tagging bugs, monitoring bugs in other
    systems, <a href="http://help.launchpad.net/MaloneHighlights">and more</a>.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
